            <subsection name="Looking for improvements! / Commit request!">
                Please don't simply copy the sourcecode from the sources packages into your own projects. Either try to
                include the package as is with the jar files
                or<a href="http://code.google.com/p/spring-security-facelets-taglib/source/checkout" target="_blank">
                checkout our source from SVN</a>, make your changes there, compile &amp; test locally
                and then provide your changes back to us! We're giving you this taglib for free,
                <strong>please give your improvements back!</strong>
            </subsection>


